('713', '1', '2017-10-11 11:22:45', '2017-10-11 11:22:45', '<h3>The Residents are an American <a class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Art collective\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Art_collective\">art collective</a> best known for avant-garde music and <a title=\"Multimedia\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multimedia\">multimedia</a> works. Since their first official release, <i><a title=\"Meet the Residents\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meet_the_Residents\">Meet the Residents</a></i> (1974), the group has released over sixty albums, numerous music videos and short films, three <a title=\"CD-ROM\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CD-ROM\">CD-ROM</a> projects, and ten <a title=\"DVD\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DVD\">DVDs</a>.</h3>', 'AAA Movers Move Estimate UX Design', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'residents', '', '', '2018-06-12 20:04:29', '2018-06-12 20:04:29', '', '0', 'http://deppo.tkdemos.com/?post_type=jetpack-portfolio&#038;p=713', '0', 'jetpack-portfolio', '', '0'),
('714', '1', '2017-04-03 10:17:29', '2017-04-03 10:17:29', '<h3>This Beautiful grid based identity belongs to Resident GP. The one-stop shop for unique, beautiful, and well-crafted designer homewares online &amp; gifts. Featuring over 40 popular home decor brands.</h3>', 'Art Gifs', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ogp__trashed', '', '', '2018-06-13 14:23:53', '2018-06-13 14:23:53', '', '0', 'http://deppo.tkdemos.com/?post_type=jetpack-portfolio&#038;p=714', '0', 'jetpack-portfolio', '', '0'),
('715', '1', '2017-10-11 11:23:59', '2017-10-11 11:23:59', '<h2>GOAL:</h2>\r\n<h3>Gyst sought out help with their at-the-time broken website. The goal was to scrap their wordpress template and start with a newly revised hand-coded web-presence with a maing focuse on the mobile experience.</h3>\r\n\r\n<h2>CHALLENGE:</h2>\r\n<h3>Since we weren\'t using the template I was challenged to start from ground zero and come up with a concept that both portrayed the message Gyst wanted to send as well as design and develop a website that performed well across devices. \r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<h2>SOLUTION:</h2>\r\n<h3>With some discussions and ideations we landed on a strategy that was simple, elegant, and informative offering a user a more direct and concise experience. Using their high quality food photos we were able to capture the elegance that they were trying to achieve. While not shying away from the bold usage of reds and blacks we were able to establish a sense of brand that was previously lost.</h3>', 'Gyst Fermentation Bar', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'gyst-fermentation-bar', '', '', '2018-06-12 20:04:21', '2018-06-12 20:04:21', '', '0', 'http://deppo.tkdemos.com/?post_type=jetpack-portfolio&#038;p=715', '0', 'jetpack-portfolio', '', '0'),
('716', '1', '2018-06-01 09:00:29', '2018-06-01 09:00:29', '<h4>Over is a clothing brand fueled by personal demand since it\'s start in 2012. The pieces we create convey the core three values which we continue to offer today — authentic, wearable and affordable clothing.</h4>', 'Vivacity Tech', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'vivacity-tech', '', '', '2018-06-11 21:21:02', '2018-06-11 21:21:02', '', '0', 'http://deppo.tkdemos.com/?post_type=jetpack-portfolio&#038;p=716', '0', 'jetpack-portfolio', '', '0'),
